---
title: Cheesy Chicken Chowder with DIY Garlic-Cheddar Croutons
description: Hearty, comforting and restorative – this dish is everything you could want in a chowder! Crispy garlic croutons top this beautiful bowl of goodness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chaudree-de-poulet-fromagee-a7a8f2e1.jpg
